{"tid":958052,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「中國人身份」認同創傘運後新低 港人對明年社會發展不樂觀","createTime":"2018-12-27T13:15:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-28T12:16:55.000Z","uid":39464,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"e8e94080614708a3f448bae4e581df41688fe3bb","tid":958052,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T13:15:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181227/large/1545908691_2467.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181227%2Flarge%2F1545908691_2467.png&h=3d605299&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港大民意研究計劃本月3至6日以電話訪問1,005名香港巿民，發現巿民對「香港人」的感覺仍然最強，有80.8分，然後是「亞洲人」74.1分、「中華民族一份子」67.3分、「世界公民」65.6分，「中國人」及「中華人民共和國國民」則分別獲62.4分及57.1分。6個認同指數中，只有「中國人」的身份指數較上次調查錄得顯著跌幅，亦是自2014年12月以來的新低。<br />\n<br />\n港大民研另一民調則於本月17至20日以電話訪問1,000名香港巿民，發現市民對來年社會發展的樂觀淨值比去年同期大幅下跌37個百分點至負27個百分點，創2008年底以來新低。巿民對香港過去一年整體發展的最新滿意比率為36%，不滿比率為37%，淨值為負1個百分點。個人層面方面，55%巿民表示過去一年活得快樂，15%表示不快樂，快樂淨值為正40個百分點。港大民研指，數字顯示巿民活得快樂，對個人前景也感到樂觀，但對社會發展顯得悲觀。而若要在繁榮、廉潔、公平、自由、福利之間作出抉擇，該民調發現，最多巿民希望香港成為廉潔乾淨的社會，其次為公平的社會。<br />\n<br />\n展望將來，41%市民認為政府來年最需要處理房屋問題，創1994年相關問題開展以來新高；認為經濟及醫療衛生問題最為迫切的分別佔12%及11%，認為最需要處理政制、福利和教育問題的則依次佔6%、4%及3%。港大民研指出，認為政制問題最需要處理的比率變化最大，由去年的15%跌9個百分點至今年的6%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181227/59076730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181227%2F59076730&d=wP1V4d3dEokp1rN2RNzFfzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=a7613b4f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181227%2F59076730&h=95a7f5fb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181227/59076730</a>"},{"pid":"873052e708a7afe7a5ee93cbc7fbbef06c628792","tid":958052,"uid":53705,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T13:19:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181227/large/1545910749_5f14.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181227%2Flarge%2F1545910749_5f14.jpg&h=9e7e5f89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n認同「中華人民共和國國民」升左<br />\n但認同「中國人」就跌左??<br />\n<br />\n理解不能<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dcc5b241d261abb01e29c108c7cbb51e5333cbe","tid":958052,"uid":35790,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T13:19:29.000Z","msg":"「中華民族一份子」67.3分<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c763a83eda8d3954e0a1ccc30f575ca83a515f9e","tid":958052,"uid":15815,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T13:23:02.000Z","msg":"喔，我很幸福、我很幸福"},{"pid":"7656f39b7c9a67b21dd3b8d69bb6a0e08453e647","tid":958052,"uid":15815,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T13:24:06.000Z","msg":"冇大灣區人揀嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9ee3c3ae46f220cd7eb7fbde7278ed9bc9ea6eb","tid":958052,"uid":36087,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"873052e708a7afe7a5ee93cbc7fbbef06c628792","tid":958052,"uid":53705,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T13:19:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181227/large/1545910749_5f14.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181227%2Flarge%2F1545910749_5f14.jpg&h=9e7e5f89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n認同「中華人民共和國國民」升左<br />\n但認同「中國人」就跌左??<br />\n<br />\n理解不能<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T13:24:15.000Z","msg":"因為連啲官都認英美澳加<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91683f3f9b51a22c7288a5b88a2ba641f8b245a5","tid":958052,"uid":152476,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"873052e708a7a